        <abstract>
            <p>Pea self-fertilisation: has forty-five varieties growing side by side.</p>
            <p>Describes seed-salting experiments: e.g., immersion in tank filled with snow. Reports some successful germinations.</p> 
<p>Made list of naturalised plants from Asa Gray’s <hi rend="italic">Manual</hi> [<hi rend="italic">of Botany</hi>] to calculate the proportions of the great families.</p> 
        </abstract>
